Turn around, take a left and walk to the box.
Keep the remote control in the box on the bed.
Take the box with remote control.
Turn around and go back to the coffeetable.
Keep the box with remote control on the right side corner of the coffeetable.

Turn around, walk straight then turn your left to reach the coffeetable.
Place the cardboard box with the remote on the coffeetable.
